{"tid":2008294,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"發現對家假文宣","createTime":"2020-05-09T02:51:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-09T05:29:10.000Z","uid":46371,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"198a4b0af8651fb20d58bf1a247ba5ae10db4128","tid":2008294,"uid":46371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T02:51:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x2yJEE0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx2yJEE0.jpg&h=0ff26210&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家小心"},{"pid":"29467ad1e843a11b8def08d2208a496a0e0fbbb8","tid":2008294,"uid":258731,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T02:52:04.000Z","msg":"【高手過招】政治專家教你打贏輿論戰 同藍絲鬧交成日鬧輸嘅你一定要睇<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2005539\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2005539</a><br />\n<br />\n35+爭取嚟做咩？35+就係攞嚟<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>罷免港共政府</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><br />\n「如果美國要求中國就中共病毒賠償，中國一定會攞各位香港人血汗錢嚟找數」</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>「如果啲一帶一路投資失敗啲非洲國家要賠償，中國一定都會攞各位香港人血汗錢嚟找數」<br />\n</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">GET MY MONEY BACK<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我要攞返我啲錢<br />\n香港人啲錢唔係比港共亂咁洗</span></span><br />\n香港納稅人財政儲備 不是中共提款機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我要攞返我啲錢</span></strong></span>」就係我哋對攬炒嘅論述<br />\n「<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>如果這是攬炒，我們不怕承認</strong></span></span>」<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>香港財政儲備絕對唔可以比中共當係提款機嚟用<br />\n唔可以攞嚟起啲濕鳩明日大嶼<br />\n唔可以攞嚟找一帶一路啲數 債務<br />\n更加唔可以攞香港啲錢嚟賠償中共病毒索償費用</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n高鐵已經有版我哋睇<br />\n高鐵造價853億沒有帶來經濟效益 卻只有贈送中共病毒（武漢肺炎）<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/Untitled-1-10_NQdC3_1200x0.png\" /><br />\n<br />\n攬抄 就是從港共手中搶返屬於我哋嘅血汗錢<br />\n<br />\n立法會35+之後就係要否決預算案<br />\n推冧港共之後再建立一個<span style=\"color: brown;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>民主主權國家<br />\n35+就是「罷免港共行動」</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n中國係中共病毒疫情之後將會比全球杯葛<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聰明嘅香港人要及時止蝕同中國割席<br />\n因為一個民主主權國家<br />\n係國際舞台先會有競爭力<br />\n先至可以同鄰近嘅星加坡，台灣一較高下</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港只要唔係民主主權國家，人哋係唔撚會show你，亦都唔會有信心返嚟香港投資</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n攬炒就是<br />\n「從港共手中搶回屬於香港人金庫」<br />\n「建立民主主權國家  才是爭取國際競爭力的致勝之道」"},{"pid":"3cca77289a6f4040a3c6e499be80dec8a892d345","tid":2008294,"uid":132010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T02:52:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6a1220410cf570ca8c4592da73e4829e1f32449f","tid":2008294,"uid":220431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T02:57:43.000Z","msg":"唔搞佢 佢自己都執啦"},{"pid":"c8b97e9ee81de088c557a5bdb9a1b3f5935cef1a","tid":2008294,"uid":46371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T03:06:19.000Z","msg":"推 岩岩同親戚大戰完 想提下d 手足"},{"pid":"cc7c7c45d8ae262a08ec40928d2d89a2945d199e","tid":2008294,"uid":168567,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T03:09:02.000Z","msg":"佢依個on9左啲<br />\n我哋點會益茶錢俾藍店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"288d4cccbb444cbd8d9018d7d226513ca1f7e703","tid":2008294,"uid":118553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T03:14:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f74177faef2cd780875de01b8cbb0dcffa718839","tid":2008294,"uid":159913,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T03:17:08.000Z","msg":"收到風整poster嗰個係美孚富臨經理<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32a610a17b11b990ae330ecb3352454bf155fab8","tid":2008294,"uid":245409,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T03:18:54.000Z","msg":"就算係都和你飲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點會係和你飲茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽落柒下柒下咁"},{"pid":"cf2c2c784b0a9deb76911abb851555eb8f7ca56b","tid":2008294,"uid":76680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T03:23:46.000Z","msg":"富臨咁唔掂咩 岩岩先攞左1億<br />\n富臨仲走去搶其他酒樓生意？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e4006e7ed7ec4dd39734ff2deb1c7f022d24ed3","tid":2008294,"uid":49669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T03:23:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35bfb856eb068ac03f4b569869277f33a756b126","tid":2008294,"uid":258948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T03:28:06.000Z","msg":"元氣就話可以$0埋單走人，酒樓要蝕茶錢，同埋依家本身酒樓十間九間都唔滿，邊個會咁天才走去幫人坐旺個場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa13dbf089b5e317163a96e75e8f99a922723714","tid":2008294,"uid":59242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T03:42:47.000Z","msg":"飲茶要比茶錢不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去Starfuck 坐好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8c13a4558b7c6c2fda8ce7ff7c081cd3e872f19","tid":2008294,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T05:29:10.000Z","msg":"富臨不了，偷工減料呃港豬"}]}